snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4415: Police Ne Di Good News
--------------------------------------------------------
As panic takes over the society, the police deliver surprising news that the matter has been resolved. How will the members react to this?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4415 | 4 June 2025
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/shows/taarak-mehta-ka-ooltah-chashmah-1090480162

snippet.title: BANANA BAJJI | Banana Fry | Valakkai Bajji Recipe  Cooking in Village | Tasty Plantain Evening Snack
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we made a delicious and crispy Banana Bajji using raw plantains, also known as Valakkai Bajji in Tamil. This traditional South Indian snack, especially in Kerala and Tamil Nadu, is a perfect evening treat, especially when served hot with tea. We sliced fresh plantains, dipped them in a flavorful gram flour batter seasoned with spices, and deep-fried them over a woodfire stove until golden and crisp.

Our village-style cooking brings out the authentic taste and aroma of this simple yet tasty snack. Watch how we prepare these bajjis in a natural outdoor setting, using fresh ingredients and traditional methods.

Enjoy the satisfying crunch and soft banana filling in every bite! Perfect for family gatherings or as a festive snack.

it.title: BAJI DI BANANE | Frittura di banane | Ricetta Valakkai Bajji Cucinare nel villaggio | Delizioso s...
it.description:
Oggi nel nostro villaggio abbiamo preparato un delizioso e croccante Banana Bajji usando platani crudi, noto anche come Valakkai Bajji in Tamil. Questo spuntino tradizionale dell'India meridionale, in particolare del Kerala e del Tamil Nadu, è una delizia perfetta per la sera, soprattutto se servito caldo con il tè. Abbiamo affettato platani freschi, li abbiamo immersi in una saporita pastella di farina di ceci condita con spezie e li abbiamo fritti su una stufa a legna fino a quando non sono diventati dorati e croccanti.

La nostra cucina in stile villaggio esalta il gusto e l'aroma autentici di questo spuntino semplice ma gustoso. Guarda come prepariamo questi bajji in un ambiente naturale all'aperto, utilizzando ingredienti freschi e metodi tradizionali.

Gusta la croccantezza appagante e il morbido ripieno di banana in ogni boccone! Perfetto per le riunioni di famiglia o come spuntino festivo.

id.title: PISANG BAJI | Gorengan Pisang | Resep Masakan Valakkai Bajji di Desa | Camilan Lezat Malam Hari d...
id.description:
Hari ini di desa kami, kami membuat Bajji Pisang yang lezat dan renyah menggunakan pisang mentah, yang juga dikenal sebagai Valakkai Bajji dalam bahasa Tamil. Camilan tradisional India Selatan ini, khususnya di Kerala dan Tamil Nadu, merupakan sajian malam yang sempurna, terutama jika disajikan hangat dengan teh. Kami mengiris pisang segar, mencelupkannya ke dalam adonan tepung gram yang beraroma dan dibumbui dengan rempah-rempah, dan menggorengnya di atas tungku kayu bakar hingga berwarna keemasan dan renyah.

Cara memasak ala desa kami menghasilkan rasa dan aroma asli dari camilan sederhana namun lezat ini. Saksikan cara kami menyiapkan bajji ini di alam terbuka, menggunakan bahan-bahan segar dan metode tradisional.

Nikmati kerenyahan yang memuaskan dan isian pisang yang lembut di setiap gigitan! Sempurna untuk acara kumpul keluarga atau sebagai camilan hari raya.

es-US.title: PLÁTANO BAJI | Plátano frito Receta de Valakkai Bajji cocinando en el pueblo | Deliciosa merienda...
es-US.description:
Hoy en nuestro pueblo, preparamos un delicioso y crujiente Bajji de Plátano con plátanos crudos, también conocido como Valakkai Bajji en tamil. Este aperitivo tradicional del sur de la India, especialmente en Kerala y Tamil Nadu, es un capricho perfecto para la tarde, sobre todo caliente con té. Cortamos plátanos frescos en rodajas, los sumergimos en una sabrosa masa de harina de garbanzos sazonada con especias y los freímos en una estufa de leña hasta que quedaron dorados y crujientes.

Nuestra cocina al estilo del pueblo realza el auténtico sabor y aroma de este sencillo pero delicioso aperitivo. Observa cómo preparamos estos bajjis en un entorno natural al aire libre, con ingredientes frescos y métodos tradicionales.

¡Disfruta de su delicioso crujido y suave relleno de plátano en cada bocado! Perfecto para reuniones familiares o como aperitivo festivo.

de-DE.title: BANANEN-BAJI | Bananen-Pommes | Valakkai Bajji-Rezept Kochen im Dorf | Leckerer Abendsnack mit Ko...
de-DE.description:
Heute haben wir in unserem Dorf ein köstliches und knuspriges Bananen-Bajji aus rohen Kochbananen zubereitet, auf Tamil auch Valakkai Bajji genannt. Dieser traditionelle südindische Snack, vor allem in Kerala und Tamil Nadu, ist ein perfekter Abendgenuss, besonders heiß serviert mit Tee. Wir haben frische Kochbananen in Scheiben geschnitten, sie in einen aromatischen Kichererbsenmehlteig getaucht und über einem Holzofen frittiert, bis sie goldbraun und knusprig waren.

Unsere dörfliche Küche bringt den authentischen Geschmack und das Aroma dieses einfachen, aber leckeren Snacks perfekt zur Geltung. Sehen Sie zu, wie wir diese Bajjis in der Natur mit frischen Zutaten und nach traditionellen Methoden zubereiten.

Genießen Sie das köstliche Knuspern und die weiche Bananenfüllung mit jedem Bissen! Perfekt für Familienfeiern oder als festlicher Snack.

ja.title: バナナバジ |バナナフライ | Valakkai Bajji レシピ 村で料理 |おいしいプランテンの夕方のおやつ
ja.description:
今日は私たちの村で、生のプランテンを使った、美味しくてサクサクのバナナ・バジを作りました。タミル語ではヴァラッカイ・バジとも呼ばれています。南インド、特にケーララ州とタミル・ナードゥ州でよく食べられるこの伝統的なスナックは、温かいお茶と一緒に食べると、夕方の楽しみにぴったりです。新鮮なプランテンをスライスし、スパイスで味付けした風味豊かなひよこ豆の粉の衣につけて、薪ストーブでこんがりと焼き色がつくまで揚げます。

私たちの村流の調理法は、このシンプルながらも美味しいスナックの本物の味と香りを引き立てます。自然の恵み豊かな屋外で、新鮮な食材と伝統的な製法を使ってバジを作る様子をご覧ください。

一口ごとに、満足感のあるサクサクとした食感と、ふわふわのバナナフィリングをお楽しみください！家族の集まりやお祝いのスナックに最適です。

hi.title: केले की बाजी | केला फ्राई | गांव में वलक्कई बज्जी पकाने की विधि | स्वादिष्ट केला शाम का नाश्ता
hi.description:
आज हमारे गांव में, हमने कच्चे केलों का उपयोग करके एक स्वादिष्ट और कुरकुरी केले की बाजी बनाई, जिसे तमिल में वलाक्काई बाजी भी कहा जाता है। यह पारंपरिक दक्षिण भारतीय नाश्ता, विशेष रूप से केरल और तमिलनाडु में, शाम के खाने के लिए एकदम सही है, खासकर जब इसे चाय के साथ गरमागरम परोसा जाए। हमने ताज़े केलों को काटा, उन्हें मसालों से भरे स्वादिष्ट बेसन के घोल में डुबोया और लकड़ी की आग पर सुनहरा और कुरकुरा होने तक डीप फ्राई किया।

हमारे गांव-शैली के खाना पकाने से इस सरल लेकिन स्वादिष्ट नाश्ते का असली स्वाद और सुगंध सामने आती है। देखें कि हम इन बाजी को प्राकृतिक बाहरी सेटिंग में, ताज़ी सामग्री और पारंपरिक तरीकों का उपयोग करके कैसे तैयार करते हैं।

हर निवाले में संतोषजनक कुरकुरेपन और नरम केले की फिलिंग का आनंद लें! पारिवारिक समारोहों या उत्सव के नाश्ते के लिए एकदम सही।

fr-FR.title: BAJI À LA BANANE | Frites de bananes | Recette de Valakkai Bajji Cuisiner dans le village | Savou...
fr-FR.description:
Aujourd'hui, dans notre village, nous avons préparé un délicieux et croustillant bajji à la banane avec des plantains crus, aussi appelé Valakkai Bajji en tamoul. Ce plat traditionnel du sud de l'Inde, notamment au Kerala et au Tamil Nadu, est un régal idéal en soirée, surtout servi chaud avec du thé. Nous avons coupé des plantains frais en tranches, les avons trempés dans une savoureuse pâte à base de farine de pois chiche et assaisonnée d'épices, puis les avons frits au feu de bois jusqu'à ce qu'ils soient dorés et croustillants.

Notre cuisine villageoise met en valeur le goût et l'arôme authentiques de ce plat simple et savoureux. Découvrez comment nous préparons ces bajjis en plein air, avec des ingrédients frais et des méthodes traditionnelles.

Savourez le croquant et la douceur de la banane à chaque bouchée ! Parfait pour les réunions de famille ou pour un goûter festif.

pt-BR.title: BANANA BAJI | Banana Frita | Receita de Valakkai Bajji cozinhando na vila | Lanche da noite sabor...
pt-BR.description:
Hoje, em nossa aldeia, preparamos um delicioso e crocante Bajji de Banana usando bananas-da-terra cruas, também conhecido como Valakkai Bajji em tâmil. Este lanche tradicional do sul da Índia, especialmente em Kerala e Tamil Nadu, é um deleite perfeito para a noite, principalmente quando servido quente com chá. Fatiamos bananas-da-terra frescas, mergulhamos em uma saborosa massa de farinha de grão-de-bico temperada com especiarias e as fritamos em um fogão a lenha até dourarem e ficarem crocantes.

Nossa culinária típica da aldeia realça o sabor e o aroma autênticos deste lanche simples, porém saboroso. Veja como preparamos estes bajjis em um ambiente natural ao ar livre, usando ingredientes frescos e métodos tradicionais.

Aprecie a crocância e o recheio macio de banana em cada mordida! Perfeito para reuniões familiares ou como um lanche festivo.

snippet.title: Tata Harrier EV AWD First Impressions | Gagan Choudhary
snippet.description:
Tata Motors finally launched their first AWD SUV in the last 5 years, Harrier.ev. It is an electric SUV that comes with Dual Motor. Tata Motors call it QWD or Qual Wheel drive. Harrier Electric will also come with RWD single motor setup as standard. The starting price of the Harrier electric 65 kWh RWD base variant is Rs 21.49 Lakh Ex-Showroom. The other battery pack is 75 kWh. This car can do 0-100 in just 6.3 seconds in Dual motor AWD trim and should give a practical range of up to 480 km in RWD single motor variant.

snippet.title: The greatest chess finish ever | Gukesh vs Magnus Carlsen | Norway Chess 2025
snippet.description:
World no.1 Magnus Carlsen and World Champion D. Gukesh clashed against each other in round 1 of Norway Chess and that game ended in Magnus' favour. We are now back for the 2nd game in the tournament, this time Gukesh has the white pieces against the Norwegian legend. Would Gukesh be able to get his revenge, or will Magnus show his class once again! Check out this amazing game along with IM Sagar Shah's commentary and enjoy the greatest chess finish that you can ever expect.

Video: ChessBase India
Shot by Aditya Sur Roy and Abhyudaya Ram, edited by Ravindra Potawad

hi.title: अब तक का सबसे शानदार शतरंज का अंत | गुकेश बनाम मैग्नस कार्लसन | नॉर्वे शतरंज 2025
hi.description:
नॉर्वे शतरंज के पहले राउंड में दुनिया के नंबर 1 मैग्नस कार्लसन और विश्व चैंपियन डी. गुकेश एक दूसरे से भिड़ गए और वह गेम मैग्नस के पक्ष में समाप्त हुआ। अब हम टूर्नामेंट के दूसरे गेम के लिए वापस आ गए हैं, इस बार गुकेश के पास नॉर्वेजियन दिग्गज के खिलाफ सफेद मोहरे हैं। क्या गुकेश अपना बदला ले पाएगा, या मैग्नस एक बार फिर अपनी क्लास दिखाएगा! आईएम सागर शाह की कमेंट्री के साथ इस अद्भुत गेम को देखें और सबसे बेहतरीन शतरंज फिनिश का आनंद लें जिसकी आप कभी उम्मीद कर सकते हैं। वीडियो: चेसबेस इंडिया
आदित्य सुर रॉय और अभ्युदय राम द्वारा शूट किया गया, रवींद्र पोटावाड द्वारा संपादित

#शतरंज #चेसबेसइंडिया #मैग्नसकार्लसन #गुकेश #नॉर्वेशेस
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ja.title: 史上最高のチェスのフィニッシュ | グケシュ vs マグヌス・カールセン | ノルウェーチェス2025
ja.description:
世界ランキング1位のマグヌス・カールセンと世界チャンピオンのD・グケシュが、ノルウェーチェスの第1ラウンドで激突し、マグヌスが勝利しました。さあ、トーナメント第2局の放送です。今回はグケシュが白駒でノルウェーのレジェンドを相手に戦いを挑みます。グケシュはリベンジできるのか、それともマグヌスが再び実力を発揮するのか！IMサガール・シャーの解説とともに、この素​​晴らしい対局を視聴し、かつてない最高のチェスのフィナーレをお楽しみください。

動画: ChessBase India
撮影: Aditya Sur Roy、Abhyudaya Ram、編集: Ravindra Potawad

#チェス #ChessBaseIndia #magnuscarlsen #gukesh #norwaychess

pt-BR.title: O melhor resultado de todos os tempos no xadrez | Gukesh vs Magnus Carlsen | Xadrez da Noruega 2025
pt-BR.description:
O número 1 do mundo, Magnus Carlsen, e o campeão mundial D. Gukesh se enfrentaram na primeira rodada do Xadrez Norueguês, e a partida terminou a favor de Magnus. Estamos de volta para a segunda partida do torneio, desta vez Gukesh com as peças brancas contra a lenda norueguesa. Será que Gukesh conseguirá se vingar ou Magnus mostrará sua classe mais uma vez? Confira esta partida incrível, acompanhada pelos comentários do IM Sagar Shah, e curta o melhor final de xadrez que você poderia esperar.

Vídeo: ChessBase Índia
Fotografado por Aditya Sur Roy e Abhyudaya Ram, editado por Ravindra Potawad

#Xadrez #ChessBaseÍndia #magnuscarlsen #gukesh #xadreznorueguês

snippet.title: Rakesh Barot | Panetar Parka Na Odhiya | પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢ્યા | New Gujarati Bewafa Song 2025
snippet.description:
Check out the new Gujarati bewafa song by Rakesh Barot, "Panetar Parka Na Odhiya" only on   @SaregamaGujarati  💔🎶

રાકેશ બારોટનું નવું ગુજરાતી બેવફા ગીત "પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢ્યા" સાંભળો, માત્ર  @SaregamaGujarati  પર.

Credits:
Singer: Rakesh Barot 
Producer: Red Velvet Cinema 
Lyrics: Prakash Vaghela 
Music: Dipesh chavada 
Artist: Rakesh Barot, Sweta Sen, Bobby Kalpesh 
Co.artist: Lata Prajapati, Dharati Patel, Sharmaji 
Dop: Arvind Motap 
Camera Attended: Kartik Thakor 
Editing: Kishor Rajput 
Concept & Director: Shankar Thakor Borisanawala
Creative Head: Dhyey Films & Team
Technical Support: Jenis Talaviya
Spot boys: Kiran Thakor, Lalo, Ajay
Makeup: Hasmukh limbachiya 
Hair Style: Bhavana Ben
Rakesh Barot Costume: Manisha R Barot
Ass.director: Babusinh Thakor
Poster design: Aman Agola
Junior Artist Management: Nayan Thakor
Production Management: Jigar Panchal 
Food Management: Village Vila cafe 
Thanks: Manish Patel, Divyang patel

Lyrics:
મારા અરમાનો ને રાખ માં તે રોળ્યા (૨)
 પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢીયા 
આજ અડધા રસ્તે સાથ તે છોડયા ..
પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢીયાં 
જીવતિ લાશ બનાવી ને છોડી રે જવના 
તારા ગયા પછી અમે નોધારા થવાના 
મારા હાચવેલાં દિલ ને તમે તોડીયા
 પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢીયાં 
મારા અરમાનો ને રાખ માં તે રોળ્યા (૨) 
પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢીયા
હો શેતર ના શેઢે રોજ મને મળવા આવતી 
તને નઈ ભૂલું એવા સોંગંધ ખાતીતી 
હો ચોરી યે ચઢતા જીવ કેમ ચાલીયો 
તારો રયો ના ખોળિયા માં પ્રાણ અમારો 
એની ઉપર તારી ચોરીયો ચીતરાવી 
અમે અમારા હાલ પર રોય 
પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢીયા ……
હો પારકા ના હાથ મા હાથ સે તમારો 
જોઈ એને બેવફા જીવ બળે મારો 
હો નજર સોમુ ફેરા ફરે ચમનું જોયું જાય રે
 નથી જવાતું મારા દિલમાં દર્દ થાય રે 
હો ખુશીયોને  તે ઠોકર રે ચઢાવી 
આખરે બેવફા તારી જાત રે બતાવી 
મારી જિંદગી મા ઝેર તે ધોળ્યા
 પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢીયા
મારા અરમાનો ને રાખ માં તે રોળ્યા (૨) 
પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢીયા….

#RakeshBarot 
#bewafasong
#saregamagujarati 
#sadsong
#newgujaratisong
#gujaratisongstatus
#gujaratisongs   
#gujarati

snippet.title: ENG vs WI | 3rd ODI | Cricket Highlights | West Indies Tour Of England | 3rd June 2025
snippet.description:
England wrapped up a dominant ODI series against the West Indies with a convincing 7-wicket victory in a rain-shortened final match at The Oval. West Indies managed a total of 251-9 in 40 overs which was chased down by the home team in just 29.4 overs. The win sealed a 3-0 whitewash, showcasing England’s depth and form ahead of the summer season. 
.

snippet.title: Vilen - Bad Trip (Official Video)
snippet.description:
‘BT' is a song about a rugged, tough guy drinking away his sorrows, his red, bloodshot eyes revealing a troubled past. Today, he's not to be messed with, as he is possibly missing an old love.


Artist : Vilen
Lyrcist : Vilen
Music : Vilen
Composer : Vilen
Director : Vilen
Screenplay : Vilen
Editor : Vilen
Colour correction : Vilen
DOP : Alex
Mix Master : Hanish Taneja
Music production : Vilen, Maniac
Recording studio : G10 Studio
Label : Darks Music Company
Starring : Vilen, BigSsmoke, Amit Om Malik, Akhil Rathee, Nitin Dabas
Location courtesy : Mnky Houz, Privee Delhi

Lyrics -
Ho ankh chadh ri ho ri kasuti laal
Laage se aaj gamm mai piwe se

Ho laage aa ri se sajan ki re yaad
Laage se aaj gamm mai piwe se

Ho ankh chadh ri ho ri kasuti laal
Laa ke peg 10 chaale sudha yaar
Laage se aaj gamm mai piwe se


Darr jaga chore ki re ankh dekh le
Makha ankh dekhle

Kisi laage se jalti aag dekhle
Makha aag dekhle

Laage se bhola aaj
Bhairav ka roop se le rhaya

2-4 bhaari bhaari
Gelyan yo bhoot bhi le rhaya

Chore hat hat ke chaale
Chori masta rahi se

Aaj suhaati na jo
Aankh matka rahi se

Aaja mardaan ke bhi halaat dekhle
Re halaat dekhle

Tadpe jo saari saari raat dekhle
Aaja raat dekhle


Ho iski kad pe jakham
Haath laal

Taare sir te jo aare se khayaal
Laage se aaj gam mai piwe se


Ho ankh chadh ri ho ri kasuti laal
Laage se aaj gamm mai piwe se

Ho laage aa ri se sajan ki re yaad
Laage se aaj gamm mai piwe se

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4414 - Mehta ke Bharose ne Toda Gokuldham Walo ka Dil?! | Taarak Mehta ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Step into Jethalal’s world with Gada Electronics!  Manage the shop, tackle quirky customers, and experience nonstop TMKOC-style fun. 

Are you ready for the challenge? 
Play now: https://gadaelectronics.page.link/dhgB  
#GadaElectronics #TMKOCGame

Watch the FULL MOVIE of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSk2_rPKNCDcjNAA8vaDN-E&si=rC5AotwLD2r3MHna

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Jheel Mehta / Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal / Monaz Mevawalla as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah / Dharmit Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: गंगा दशहरा विशेष: Ganga Dussehra Special Bhajans | LAKHBIR SINGH LAKKHA, ANURADHA PAUDWAL,SONU NIGAM
snippet.description:
🌹🪔🙏गंगा दशहरा की हार्दिक शुभकामनाएँ🙏🌹🪔   गंगा दशहरा पर माँ गंगे की पूजा करने और गंगा स्नान करने का महत्व है | मान्यता है कि इस दिन गंगा स्नान करने से पूरे वर्ष गंगा स्नान का फल मिलता है । इस दिन गंगा सहित पवित्र नदियों और तीर्थों में स्नान करने से विशेष पुण्य मिलता है और पापों का नाश होता है। तो आईये इस शुभ अवसर पर माँ गंगा को समर्पित इन अनुपम भजनों का आनंद लें 🙏🪔🌹भवसागर के थपेड़ों से संतप्त और सुख दुख के बंधनों में भटकता अज्ञानी मानव जब श्रद्धा भक्ति पूर्वक माँ गंगा की शरण लेता है तो उसके समस्त पाप नष्ट हो जाते हैं संसार के आकर्षण भरे प्रलोभनों से मुंह मोड़ कर जब मनुष्य सच्चे मन से भगवती भागीरथी का आश्रय लेता है तो उसका अंतरबाह्य जीवन निर्मल पावन बन जाता है ऐसी है वरदानी और कल्याणमयी माँ गंगा 🙏🙏🌹🌹🪔🪔
गंगा जिसके दर्शन मात्र से ही मानव को मुक्ति प्राप्त हो जाती है सदियों से प्रवाहित गंगा की पावन निर्मल शीतल धारा भारत भूमि पर दूर-दूर तक अपने तट पर बसने वाले जनमानस को तृप्त करती आ रही है गोमुख से गंगासागर तक की लंबी यात्रा में अनेक नगर और गांव गंगा के आंचल में बसे हुए हैं सभी धर्मों के लोग गंगा को श्रद्धा और आदर की दृष्टि से देखते हैं तथा वे इसे मोक्षदायिनी भी मानते हैं ऐसी मोक्षदायिनी पापों को हरने वाली दयामई गंगा मैया को कोटि-कोटि प्रणाम गंगे नमामि नमामि गंगे🙏🙏
🙏🪔https://youtu.be/5Sw3a6G51pY🙏🪔
Subscribe: http://www.youtube.com/tseriesbhakti

गंगा जिसके दर्शन मात्र से ही मानव को मुक्ति प्राप्त हो जाती है सदियों से प्रवाहित गंगा की पावन निर्मल शीतल धारा भारत भूमि पर दूर-दूर तक अपने तट पर बसने वाले जनमानस को तृप्त करती आ रही है गोमुख से गंगासागर तक की लंबी यात्रा में अनेक नगर और गांव गंगा के आंचल में बसे हुए हैं सभी धर्मों के लोग गंगा को श्रद्धा और आदर की दृष्टि से देखते हैं तथा वे इसे मोक्षदायिनी भी मानते हैं ऐसी मोक्षदायिनी पापों को हरने वाली दयामई गंगा मैया को कोटि-कोटि प्रणाम गंगे नमामि नमामि गंगे🙏🙏

snippet.title: Women ki Duniya | Take A Break
snippet.description:
Welcome to Women Ki Duniya — a hilarious sketch that flips the script on gender roles! 🤯
What if women were the dominant gender in society? In this fun, satirical world, men are the ones being told to “smile more,” struggling to get promoted, and balancing office work and house chores — while women run the show with power, sass, and zero tolerance for mansplaining. 😎💅
From office meetings to family functions, this sketch hilariously reimagines everyday situations with the gender dynamics reversed, making you laugh and think at the same time!
Watch now and enter a world where patriarchy gets a taste of its own medicine! 💥

#WomenKiDuniya #ComedySketch #WhatIfWomenRuled #GenderSwap #Satire #RelatableHumor #WomenPower #DesiSketch #RoleReversal

en-IN.description:
Welcome to Women Ki Duniya — a hilarious sketch that flips the script on gender roles! 🤯
What if women were the dominant gender in society? In this fun, satirical world, men are the ones being told to “smile more,” struggling to get promoted, and balancing office work and house chores — while women run the show with power, sass, and zero tolerance for mansplaining. 😎💅
From office meetings to family functions, this sketch hilariously reimagines everyday situations with the gender dynamics reversed, making you laugh and think at the same time!
Watch now and enter a world where patriarchy gets a taste of its own medicine! 💥

#WomenKiDuniya #ComedySketch #WhatIfWomenRuled #GenderSwap #Satire #RelatableHumor #WomenPower #DesiSketch #RoleReversal

Produced By - Monica Prabhudesai
Creative Producer- Ravindra Sarowar

Writer - Praja Sanghmitra
Director - Aparna Tandale
Associate Director - Satyam Phule

तुमने मुझे इतना बड़ा धोका दिया, पैसो के बदले मेरा मकान गिरवी रखा - Om Jai Jagdish -  ज़बरदस्त बेस्ट सीन - Anil Kapoor, Abhishek Bachchan - Om Jai Jagdish - 

Witness the heartwarming story of brotherhood and family values in "Om Jai Jagadish." Released in 2002, this Hindi film beautifully portrays the lives of three brothers and their unwavering bond despite facing various trials and tribulations. When their father passes away, the eldest brother, Om, selflessly takes on the responsibility of caring for his younger siblings, Jai and Jagadish. As they navigate life's challenges, including financial difficulties and personal aspirations, their unity is tested. Will their strong familial love withstand the pressures of the outside world? Experience a captivating narrative filled with emotion, drama, and memorable performances from a stellar cast.

◾ Film : Om Jai Jagadish.
◾ Director : Anupam Kher.
◾ Producer : Vashu Bhagnani.
◾ Cast : Anil Kapoor, Fardeen Khan, Abhishek Bachchan, Mahima Chaudhry, Urmila Matondkar, Pooja Batra.

snippet.title: Squid Game: Season 3 | Official Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
Every game must come to an end.
Squid Game. The final season. June 27.
Only on Netflix.

More info on Squid Game Season 3:
A failed rebellion, the death of a friend, and a secret betrayal. Picking up in the aftermath of Season 2’s bloody cliffhanger, the third and final season of Netflix’s most popular series finds Gi-hun, a.k.a. Player 456, at his lowest point yet. But the Squid Game stops for no one, so Gi-hun will be forced to make some important choices in the face of overwhelming despair as he and the surviving players are thrust into deadlier games that test everyone’s resolve. With each round, their choices lead to increasingly grave consequences. Meanwhile, In-ho resumes his role as Front Man to welcome the mysterious VIPs, and his brother Jun-ho continues his search for the elusive island, unaware there’s a traitor in their midst. Will Gi-hun make the right decisions, or will Front Man finally break his spirit?
Director Hwang Dong-hyuk, who made history at the 74th Primetime Emmys®, becoming the first Asian to win Outstanding Directing for a Drama Series, once again helms the series as director, writer, and producer. Season 3 stars Lee Jung-jae, Lee Byung-hun, Yim Si-wan, Kang Ha-neul, Wi Ha-jun, Park Gyu-young, Park Sung-hoon, Yang Dong-geun, Kang Ae-sim, Jo Yu-ri, Chae Kuk-hee, Lee David, Roh Jae-won, and Jun Suk-ho, with special appearance by Park Hee-soon.

#TUDUM

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81615967

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Squid Game: Season 3 | Official Trailer | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

Devastated after losing his friend, Player 456 presses on — challenging the Front Man's scheme in the final season of the globally most-watched series.

snippet.title: Indians And Summer Season | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hello guys
This Video has all the things that happen in Indians And Summer Season . 

To buy Himalaya SunProtect+ here is the link of  - https://amzn.to/4iRtiwe

Every Indian in summer vacations going on vacation with family to hill stations like shimla , manali , mussoorie , darjeeling , haridwar , Rishikesh . Indian Aunties going on vacation on their girls trip to south inida exploring Karnataka , loving Bangalore monsoon weather , south indian food of mysore , dosa , idli , vada , appum  , shopping in local markets for their kids and missing them . Childhood memories of eating icecream kulfi , playing with street dogs , Garmi and light jana , mosquitoes in summers and fav ac wala room , electricity bill rising because of ac , mom obsessed with bijli ka bill , Cousins and their night stay at mosi house enjoying mango shake , playing uno cards , discussing horror ghost stories , bhoot ki baaten and creating memories , Swimming class sessions in summers , playing in swimming sessions . Trip with College friends and school friends , exploring the hotel room , collecting toiletries to take back home , clicking photos and alot of gossip . Kaamwali bai asking for vacation Dilli ki sadi garmi , putting up mini swimming pool for the kids in home cause Delhi summers are dry . Indian moms dealing with holiday homework given by school teachers during summer break , Family trips , horse ridding , trekking , hiking . watching sunsets , sunrise at famous hill tops , creating memories clicking pictures , tourist locations and rush of people and traffic jams , mother excited to go vacation getting her beauty regime by parlour didi , waxing , facial , threading , bleach , dtan , shopping from sarojini nagar to travel , buying gifts for relatives on vacay , travelling by train enjoying , singing eating train food , road trip with family , stopping at dhaba , mom feeding her home cooked food puri aloo jeera sabzi , middle class dad driving on highway , kids singing fighting taking pictures on the way to Himachal and so much more ..
This video is filled with such memories and situations we all have been in. 

Relish and Relive your Childhood Memories.. You will have major nostalgia
Do share it with your friends and family especially guests .. Comment down your Fav Part, 
Like, Share and 
Subscribe to our Channel - http://bit.ly/thepaayaljain | Press Bell Icon

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Sakharam के लौटने से झूम उठा Bhide | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | 1 Jun 2025
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

Bhide is seeing at the cheque collection for the society maintenance and sees that Jetha's cheque is missing. He decides to go to Jetha's house to ask for it. When he is going there, he realises that Sakharam is not there and presents a monologue to him. Just then, Jetha comes for his morning rituals and the vessel in his hand slips and falls on Bhide's head. This sparks an argument between the two.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episode No - 3050
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Click Here To Watch More Episodes Of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?
list=PLfyXOEyr93G3QQIKGExbP8b1NqpJKa_xb

snippet.description:
Teen Sitaray is also called Three Sister or Uc Kiz Kardes is a Turkish Drama in Urdu Dubbing & Hindi Dubbing

🎉 Subscribe to https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC_LdgZiGPqhvkOlSQR1H1cA/‬ Youtube Channel

Three Sisters (Üç Kız Kardeş) | A Heartfelt Tale of Love, Secrets & Sisterhood | Urdu Dubbed Turkish Drama

🌿 Set in the scenic coastal town of Ayvalık, Three Sisters tells the deeply emotional story of Türkan, Dönüş, and Derya—three sisters raised in a loving, close-knit family. Their childhood felt like a fairy tale, filled with dreams, warmth, and hope. But as they step into adulthood, life takes a darker, more complex turn.

As secrets unravel and painful truths come to light, each sister is forced to confront betrayal, illness, lost dreams, and the consequences of difficult choices. Through all the heartbreak and healing, one question lingers—can time really heal every wound?

Based on the bestselling novel by İclal Aydın, Three Sisters (Üç Kız Kardeş) is a beautifully written Turkish drama series dubbed in Urdu, capturing the beauty and heartbreak of sisterhood, love, and family bonds.

📌 Drama Information:
🌟 Drama Title : Teen Sitaray
🎬 Original Turkish Title: Üç Kız Kardeş

📺 Genre: Emotional Drama | Family | Romance
👫 Main Cast: Reha Özcan,İclal Aydın,Özgü Kaya

Three Sisters (Üç Kız Kardeş) | A Heartfelt Tale of Love, Secrets & Sisterhood | Urdu Dubbed Turkish Drama

🌿 Set in the scenic coastal town of Ayvalık, Three Sisters tells the deeply emotional story of Türkan, Dönüş, and Derya—three sisters raised in a loving, close-knit family. Their childhood felt like a fairy tale, filled with dreams, warmth, and hope. But as they step into adulthood, life takes a darker, more complex turn.

As secrets unravel and painful truths come to light, each sister is forced to confront betrayal, illness, lost dreams, and the consequences of difficult choices. Through all the heartbreak and healing, one question lingers—can time really heal every wound?

Based on the bestselling novel by İclal Aydın, Three Sisters (Üç Kız Kardeş) is a beautifully written Turkish drama series dubbed in Urdu, capturing the beauty and heartbreak of sisterhood, love, and family bonds.

snippet.title: 'വേടന്റെ അമ്മയാണെന്ന് എനിക്ക് ആദ്യം അറിയില്ലായിരുന്നു,എന്റെ മകൻ പാട്ടുകാരനാണെന്ന് മാത്രമാണ് പറഞ്ഞത്'
snippet.description:
'വേടന്റെ അമ്മയാണെന്ന് എനിക്ക് ആദ്യം അറിയില്ലായിരുന്നു... എന്റെ മകൻ പാട്ടുകാരനാണെന്ന് മാത്രമാണ് പറഞ്ഞത്... അവൻ വലിയ പാട്ടുകാരനായാൽ ഞങ്ങൾ രക്ഷപ്പെടുമെന്ന് പറഞ്ഞു, അതൊന്നും കാണാൻ അമ്മയ്ക്ക് ഭാ​ഗ്യമില്ലാതെ പോയി'; കോഴിക്കോട് നടന്ന പരിപാടിക്കിടെ മരിച്ചു പോയ അമ്മയുടെ ഫോട്ടോ വേടന് സമ്മാനമായി നൽകി യുവതി Woman gives photo of deceased mother to Vedan as gift during Kozhikode event

#MalayalamNewsLive #MalayalamLatestNews #MediaoneLive #MalayalamLatest #NewsMalayalam 

MediaOne is a 24x7 news channel which broadcasts the updated news from trustworthy sources. The fastest-growing channel with varied presentations makes the channel unique. So stay tuned with MediaOne for the latest updates that are happening around the world.

കേരളത്തിലെ ഏറ്റവും മികച്ച വാര്‍ത്താ നെറ്റ്‌വര്‍ക്കാണ് മീഡിയവണ്‍. മൂല്യാധിഷ്ഠിതവും സ്വതന്ത്രവുമായ മാധ്യമപ്രവർത്തനം നടത്തുന്ന മലയാള ന്യൂസ് ടെലിവിഷൻ ചാനലാണിത്‌.  24 മണിക്കൂറും ലോകത്തിന്‍റെ ഏത് ഭാഗത്ത് നിന്നും ഇവിടെ തത്സമയം കാണാം. അതിവേഗം വാര്‍ത്താ വീഡിയോകള്‍ ലഭിക്കാൻ മീഡിയവണ്‍ സബ്സ്ക്രൈബ് ചെയ്യാം.

-------------------------
Lyrics : - 
-------------------------
स्थाई ~ मेरी गाड़ी, मेरा बंगला, मेरा पैसा, सब तेरा,
सब कुछ तेरो सरकार मेरा तो कुछ भी नहीं 
सब कुछ तेरो सांवरिया सेठ मेरा तो कुछ भी नहीं -2

                         म्यूजिक 
अन्तरा ~ 1 यह प्लॉट, रोकड़ नोट, सांवरिया का हैं, सपोर्ट
मेरे बिजनेस में तेरा हाथ मेरा तो कुछ भी नहीं
मैं तो पुतला हूं सांवरिया सेठ चाबी तेरे हाथ में रखी

अन्तरा ~ मेरी शॉप, चले टॉप, बिजनेस दिया तुझे सोप 
मैं तो चाकर हुं तेरो रे सांवरिया मेरा तो कुछ भी नहीं
मैं तो दर खा हूं तेरा रे भिखारी मेरा तो कुछ भी नहीं 

                         म्यूजिक 
अन्तरा ~ 2 मेरा सोना, मेरी चांदी, दुनिया तो है दीवानी
खाली हाथ आए सरकार मेरा तो कुछ भी नहीं
सब तेरो रे सांवरिया सेठ मेरा तो कुछ भी नहीं

अन्तरा ~ मेरे बच्चे, तेरे पर्चे, तू उठावे घर खर्चे
मैं तो बालक हूं तेरा अनजान मेरा तो कुछ भी नहीं
सब तेरी कृपा हैं सेठ मेरा तो कुछ भी नहीं

                         म्यूजिक
अन्तरा ~ 3 मेरा खेत, मेरा लहसुन, मेरी अम्मल, मेरा कंबल
सब कुछ तेरो सरकार मेरा तो कुछ भी नहीं
सब तेरो सांवरिया सेठ मेरा तो कुछ भी नहीं

अन्तरा ~ मेरा मन, मेरा धन, मेरा तन, है अर्पण,
सब कुछ तेरो सरकार मेरा तो कुछ भी नहीं
सब तेरो रे सांवरिया सेठ मेरा तो कुछ भी नहीं

                         म्यूजिक
अन्तरा ~ 4 मारुति नंदन, गौशाला, तू है गायों का गोपाला
यह भी तू जाने और तेरा काम मेरा तो कुछ भी नहीं
सब गायों का रखना ध्यान में तो कुछ जानू नहीं

अन्तरा ~ मेरे गाने, तुम चलाते, इंस्टा फेसबुक पर छाते हैं 
यह भी तेरे सांवरिया सेठ मेरा तो कुछ भी नहीं
मेरे डीजे पर तेरा नाम वह भी मेरा नहीं 

                        म्यूजिक 
अन्तरा ~ 5 यह स्टूडियो तेरा बॉस चाहे फायदा दो या लॉस
गोकुल कहता सच्ची बात मेरा तो कुछ भी नहीं
सब सेठु के तुम सरताज मंडफिया सा और नहीं

अन्तरा ~ मेरी गाड़ी, मेरा बंगला, मेरा पैसा, सब तेरा,
सब कुछ तेरो सरकार मेरा तो कुछ भी नहीं 
सब कुछ तेरो सांवरिया सेठ मेरा तो कुछ भी नहीं

snippet.title: Man Mela - 4K Video - Gopal Bharwad - Jigar Studio - Latest Gujarati Romantic Song 2025
snippet.description:
Song: Man Mela
Singer: Gopal Bharwad
Artists: Samarth Sharma, Riddhi Tailor, Spandan Kumar
Music: Arjit Joshi
Lyrics: AD Bhadramali, Vasu Charamata
D.O.P. - Edit: Montu Rajput
Concept & Director: Anand Mayur Mehra
Producer: Gunvant Thakor
Music Label & Copyright: Jigar Studio

Lyrics:
Ke Mari Zindagi Na Har Pal
Have Tari Sathe Vitavava Chhe
Ke Mara Sapna Na Aa Mahel
Have Tara Hathe Sajavava Chhe
Ke Rangthi Bharyo Moralo
Aa Todale Jai Betho
Aa Koyal Kero Manakho
Na Jane Shu Kai Betho
Ke Divaso Malakata Jay Dhun Aabhe Chhavay

Tara Hare J Thay Man Mela
Ke Aaje Fulada Veray Mara Manada Gheray

Tara Hare Lidha Chhe Chaar Fera

Ho Kale Gheli Vaato Ma Chand Mulakato Ma

Khovai Rahyu Chhe Aa Dil
Jetla Vadhya Chhe Shwash Zindagi Na

Ek Pan Na Lau Tara Vin
Ke Raaho Mali Chhe Dil Ne
Ek Tara Chhe Sapana
Tu Jo Male To Mujane
Jaine Fale Shamana
Ke Hotho Malakata Jay Taro Cheharo Dekhay

Dil Dil Hari Jay Tari Same
Ke Rato Jagi Ne Jay Man Man Ma J Gay

Prem No Rog Lagyo Ajane

Ho Nayan Ma Bhari Lau
Man Thi Hu Vaari Jau
Jove Aa Aankho Tane Jya
Hath Laine Hatho Ma Chandani Rato Ma

Tara Thaine Rehvu Sayaba
Ke Shabdo Nathi Je Tujne
Karshe Bayan Lagani
Varasho Ahi Jashe Viti
Jo Kahish Hu Aa Dil Ni
Ke Divaso Malakata Jay Dhun Aabhe Chhavay

Tara Hare J Thay Man Mela
Ke Aaje Fulada Veray
Mara Manada Gheray
Tara Hare Lidha Chhe Chaar Fera

Ho Prem Thi Vadhare Tane Prem Me Karyo Chhe Kadi

Virah Ni Lavata Na Vaat
Aa Shwasho Thi Vadhare Tara Ratan Karya Chhe Vhali

Chhodata Na Maro Sangath

Explore the Dark Days Scenery and transform your Village into a crooked cityscape that's truly a mischief maker's paradise. Meet some shady characters as you take on unique challenges and positively wicked Events!

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

snippet.title: Yeh Kahaani Ap Sab Ki - Gyan Gaming | Teaser
snippet.description:
Notes : I’ve been playing Free Fire since 2017 – that’s seven years of dedication, passion, and countless memories and also I am the Oldest free fire Indian YouTuber till now . But over time, especially since 2021, I’ve witnessed something deeply disappointing: the gradual decline of the game I once loved, particularly on the Indian server.

Let me be clear — updates are meant to enhance a game, not break it. Sadly, it feels like each new update is pushing Free Fire further away from what made it special. And the reason? In my view, it’s the poor handling by the current Free Fire India moderation team.

Instead of focusing on what the community truly wants, these moderators seem more interested in their own agendas. Creativity, innovation, and a deep understanding of gaming culture — these are essential traits for any successful game development team. Unfortunately, the current staff appears to lack all three.

Back in 2021, Free Fire was thriving. The gameplay, events, and community engagement were all on point. But today? Unbalanced updates, pay-to-win elements, a lack of genuine player feedback integration, and overall mismanagement have caused a steep decline.
I also think that free fire partner program is most corrupted . Free fire partner YouTubers are act like a slave . Even if the game is dead, they will say nothing . They are just happy with the salary and stuffs you provided them . They don’t even think about the game . They don’t talk where need to improve. They just clowns .

As a lifelong gamer who’s experienced countless titles across all platforms, I know what makes a game engaging and sustainable. And right now, Free Fire India is heading in the wrong direction.

In my upcoming video, I’ll be breaking down exactly how the game is being ruined, point by point, and what can be done to fix it. It’s time we speak up – not because we hate the game, but because we love it and want to see it thrive again.

Garena, if you truly care about the future of Free Fire in India, it’s time to replace the current moderators with a team that listens, creates, and cares.
